Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.43,0:00:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中的誓言无法作假
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.28,0:00:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修·兰佩洛奇的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.76,0:00:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为母亲报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.41,0:00:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并创造一个妹妹娜娜莉能幸福生活的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.63,0:00:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.91,0:00:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他获得了Geass的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.65,0:00:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.93,0:00:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他化身为ZERO而行动着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.51,0:00:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.68,0:00:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对当时的鲁路修来说 这就是真实
